Author: janescandycanes
Text: haha yup. there’s no weight left on my body but i can’t eat anymore. i literally can’t. my stomach rejects it and i throw up if i eat more than 500 cals in one go. one shot and i’m flying.. because i can’t eat. EDs aren’t glamorous. you won’t be happy at your ugw.
